subject: RE: [junit] new to junit
msgSnippet: My strongest recommendation is to start by reading all the relevant links listed on the JUnit Documentation page: http://junit.sourceforge.net/#Documentation
messageBody:
My strongest recommendation is to start by reading all the relevant
links listed on the JUnit Documentation page:

http://junit.sourceforge.net/#Documentation

Including the JUnit FAQ. If that's not enough for you, there are some
really good JUnit books on the market, "JUnit in Action" and "JUnit
Recipes" being two of my own favorites.


Todd.
